item.title: Analysis on Various Commodities
item.description: Project overview In this project learned about time series analysis using deep learning =, also learned how to built a scraper which can scrape data based on respective timeline provided and can give output in csv or excel file. improved my visualization skills using seaborn Analytic Insights From Last 5 Years ● Crude Oil prices is strongly correlated with Brent Oil and Natural Gas ● Crude Oil prices is positively correlated with Copper.
